http-response-jq ^https:\/\/app\.zhuanzhuan\.com\/zz\/transfer\/getmymoretools$ 'walk(if type == "object" and .name == "免流量特权" then empty else . end) | del(.respData.groupList[] | select(.groupName == "活动参与" or .groupName == "金融工具"))'
